[% WRAPPER 'layout.tt' title="Account Created" %]

[% WRAPPER 'components/box.tt' header="Account Created" %]
    <p>Congratulations, your new account has been created and you are now logged into MusicBrainz!</p>

    <p>Please <a href="[% c.uri_for('/user/edit') %]">update your profile</a> when you get time, to let other editors know a bit more about you.</p>

    [% IF emailed %]
        <p>Since you have provided an email address, an email verification mail has been sent to <code>[% email_address %]</code>. Please check your mailbox and click on the link in the email to verify the new email address.</p>
    [% END %]

    <p>You may proceed to <a href="[% c.uri_for('/user/profile') %]">your user profile</a>, or maybe you want to [% INCLUDE 'components/doc-link.tt' to="HowEditingWorks" text="start editing!" %]</p>
[% END %]

[% END %]
